data.description: Welcome to this stunning, like new, modern and completely updated home. This cozy home is move in ready with new paint, new lighting fixtures, modern updated kitchen, and beautiful LVP flooring throughout the home. You will love the open floorplan. The beautiful, updated bathrooms feature modern fixtures, cabinetry and high-quality materials including marble, slate and porcelain. This gem sits on a LARGE and FLAT lot perfect for entertaining and playtime! Close to schools, shopping, parks and interstate. Per Seller: New roof installed in 2020, New HVAC system and digital thermostat installed in 2023.
